 think I'll need any new CSS since the existing styles should cover the match list layout. Now I'm ready to start making the actual changes to both files. I'll need to update CoinflipContext to add the claimable matches state and the select callback, then wire those into CoinflipPage to handle the UI interactions.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":3091,"cache_read_input_tokens":70101,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":3091},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"73651d8d-ca1a-4f9e-b9b7-f2b958b23ec2","uuid":"3744d46d-3bb8-420b-9afe-786e9439f2ee"}
